{"tid":1808164,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇讀心理學既朋友幫幫手","createTime":"2020-01-02T08:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T07:13:32.000Z","uid":251304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58c5ec7cb3ad5ac312021b0c77733f5ed5ab4a95","tid":1808164,"uid":251304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"近兩年發現自己對身邊既事情冇咩感覺，成日睇野好似從第三者既角度睇，好唔真實，記性理解能力愈黎愈差，想喊果陣一d都喊唔出。<br />\n<br />\n覺得情況愈黎愈嚴重，試過睇醫生，但都係比藥我食，病情好似仲嚴重左，有冇厲害既高手可以解答到我🙏"},{"pid":"0a098c8d84ce7e7859a1e6242998ac4ec35ae6c5","tid":1808164,"uid":210506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef9281b66c235dc19fee66e144de29be279321d","tid":1808164,"uid":287989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"聽你咁講有d似Dissociative disorder ， 有無搵過CP 傾？"},{"pid":"decf234abd6973220025d519283863518ec426b3","tid":1808164,"uid":251304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef9281b66c235dc19fee66e144de29be279321d","tid":1808164,"uid":287989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"聽你咁講有d似Dissociative disorder ， 有無搵過CP 傾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"請問CP姐係咩🙏有冇好建議點做"},{"pid":"b682ada6d0bcf361e549ea27b3a84a908382ba8c","tid":1808164,"uid":251304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a098c8d84ce7e7859a1e6242998ac4ec35ae6c5","tid":1808164,"uid":210506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇嘗試解決過？"},{"pid":"108687e51fa5c1a901656a84f0da0974bcbfdd9e","tid":1808164,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"換另一個精神科醫生"},{"pid":"a557dd041cf30fba18c1d8917d39707c5e5a1746",